description: Reserved matters application pursuant to P2058.08 for the demolition of 190 residential units (33 to 125 Chantry Way, 26 to 88 Walden House, 2 to 40 Roman Close, Deasley House and Perry House) and erection of 124 new residential units in 5 blocks accessed from Lower Mardyke Avenue, South Street and Walden Avenue, together with a communal commercial hub and landscaped square, landscaping and parking areas.
